{"tid":44244,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"盲亨個女失蹤！快幫手搵","createTime":"2016-12-18T06:24:59.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-21T02:02:24.000Z","uid":41126,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"5790e6c90f61cbef6ab85b7858d8dbb75d260c76","tid":44244,"uid":41126,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-18T06:24:59.000Z","msg":"一名叫Kelvin Wong的網民，昨日在小心駕駛facebook群組出帖，說水房猛人盲亨的年幼女兒，五日前在屯門或元朗失蹤。如有人知道這名小妹妹的蹤影，可聯絡一名叫家俊的男子。 <br />\n<br />\n記者今早致電家俊查詢，他承認失蹤的小妹妹確是盲亨女兒，但估計她多數是貪玩躲在朋友家中，應沒有生命危險，但都希望能盡快尋回她。至於小妹妹為何失蹤，他們仍未知道原因。記者正嘗試聯絡盲亨，希望了解事件。 <br />\n<br />\n盲亨近年一直是非多多，早年在街被打，佔中期間又因政見問題被同門排斥，兒子又曾涉及官非。<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/o9tDqkf.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fo9tDqkf.jpg&h=9fffe0c5&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2016/12/18/142451_abd32657ae2ac5467602fd600532dafc.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2016%2F12%2F18%2F142451_abd32657ae2ac5467602fd600532dafc.jpg&h=bd4970d0&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"9e36a0a01d1a4942f6232f3c68491732028462e4","tid":44244,"uid":40628,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-18T06:29:41.000Z","msg":"佔領嗰陣有咩政見？"},{"pid":"d68a7a9a4f415059182a1be20fe3ca08c9bd0176","tid":44244,"uid":2110,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-18T06:32:31.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>佔領嗰陣有咩政見？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n好似係黃絲"},{"pid":"c10e8add8401ebbc9f7e3bba3240aafc1d7e4b83","tid":44244,"uid":20943,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-18T06:36:18.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>佔領嗰陣有咩政見？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n好似係黃絲</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n佢話玩夠就好返歸喎 印象中"},{"pid":"751638215b5f6674d31f0bb86a925c31f6d0f6e2","tid":44244,"uid":47823,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-18T06:44:03.000Z","msg":"係咪靚坤做架？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/41.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d90a34d000cc4f437aa1ef5e98069ac01d1fd195","tid":44244,"uid":27151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-18T06:49:40.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>佔領嗰陣有咩政見？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n好似係黃絲</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n佢話玩夠就好返歸喎 印象中</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n但佔旺頭幾日有班mk仔開車黎幫手做路障, 果班好似係佢d馬仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n同埋我記得佢撐過gphone反國教<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b414b4d3eae972db4e5b4eea6b85a1c57e7b91f1","tid":44244,"uid":33878,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-18T06:59:23.000Z","msg":"喂柒頭留名呀我屌你老母"},{"pid":"2b8bc15a3cf764bc6e887a61cf09db284bf8f767","tid":44244,"uid":5077,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-18T07:12:13.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>佔領嗰陣有咩政見？</blockquote><br />\n好似係黃絲</blockquote><br />\n佢話玩夠就好返歸喎 印象中</blockquote><br />\n但佔旺頭幾日有班mk仔開車黎幫手做路障, 果班好似係佢d馬仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n同埋我記得佢撐過gphone反國教<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"http://upload.lsforum.net/users/public/a11936triadlovntryi224.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fupload.lsforum.net%2Fusers%2Fpublic%2Fa11936triadlovntryi224.jpg&h=fed26c87&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"afe7ba111f006eae303f5a9272127e3b7a4c03e2","tid":44244,"uid":14103,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-18T07:15:03.000Z","msg":"好 會幫手留意下 但係遮住左個樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c0fe8f86bcf4b07f992ccf4e6ec79dc12f983804","tid":44244,"uid":10094,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-18T07:32:25.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>佔領嗰陣有咩政見？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n好似係暗底黃絲 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c2173ee2e0ead054beb5b55f98c8f19c7ca6c437","tid":44244,"uid":32832,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-18T07:35:04.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>好 會幫手留意下 但係遮住左個樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 咪係"},{"pid":"6495fc5c0cc8fd85f6a09f9526302628d4e230b5","tid":44244,"uid":11694,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-18T07:45:51.000Z","msg":"同之前個台灣神手畫三張小火柴尋人有咩分別<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3f0dba89462a34998833e9598a48fd1fce09f003","tid":44244,"uid":41126,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-18T10:16:02.000Z","msg":"盲亨個女去左邊？"},{"pid":"22b75b2e6f7badc2b3bd00c875f4c8776d4481cc","tid":44244,"uid":14103,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-18T10:43:38.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>好 會幫手留意下 但係遮住左個樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 咪係</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3d7c7e4f217f524f0fbf66eee9b72972f94d0b51","tid":44244,"uid":63119,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-21T01:27:21.000Z","msg":"報紙賣左荃灣浮屍就係佢個女"},{"pid":"d8cc2dfc6d05651080206ddd0d0a9c5142b8b951","tid":44244,"uid":2613,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-21T01:39:51.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>報紙賣左荃灣浮屍就係佢個女</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n【星島日報報道】警方重案組正調查車神「盲亨」離奇失蹤的十六歲女兒，上周四浮屍荃灣碧海的案件。消息指，案發前兩天，死者的男友亦在青衣碼頭獲救，當時有人聲稱玩手機不慎墮海，未提及女友，警方揭案中案感事態可疑，正追尋該男子下落。疼愛女兒的「盲亨」昨認屍後確定女兒身分，悲痛自責，發誓要兇手無好日子過。<br />\n<br />\n佢男友<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1b4c470a75eb520d9ebf052aad2511cc68357942","tid":44244,"uid":6192,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-21T01:43:13.000Z","msg":"<block